javac.comp

类 Annotate.AnnotateRepeatedContext<T extends Attribute.Compound>

  • java.lang.Object
    • javac.comp.Annotate.AnnotateRepeatedContext<T>
  • 封闭类:
    Annotate

    public class Annotate.AnnotateRepeatedContext<T extends Attribute.Compound>
extends java.lang.Object
    This context contains all the information needed to synthesize new annotations trees by the completer for repeating annotations.
